TopicTitle: 7 Kerbal Mission to Laythe and Back

Articles.Content: I took 7 Kerbals to Laythe, landed 6, and brought them all back! Let me know what you think! I used the Bobcat Industries Parts Pack.

Very cool mission and excellent video presentation. You got a new subscriber out of that.

I'm unfamiliar with the Bobcat parts pack. I only know about some cool 1-piece landers from many versions ago that I've been afraid to use, and the Historical Rockets pack. And I was confused because in the VAB, the info box for most of the parts you touched said they were Firespitter (which I do have) and didn't look a thing like them.

BTW, I really enjoyed the demolition derby docking in the 2nd clip
Thanks! The Bobcat stuff is great, especially the 3M parts!

Thanks! The Bobcat stuff is great, especially the 3M parts!

Do these mods have names I can search for on Spaceport?

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/0-18-1-mpss-nautilus/ Here is the Ring and Fly

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/0-18-1-h-o-m-e-start-kit/ Here is the HOME Pack

Enjoy!!
Thanks. I take it the 18.1 parts work in 21.1?
Yeah they should work! I think the descriptions have anything that hasn't been fully updated on his parts packs too.
